        "username": "李瑞环",
        "uid": "33525"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t挺好的，虽然不能说有多主流，但是起码比站长被抓被封的友站相比，给人以足够的安全感。<br/>\n<br/>\n加速主义不能说是主流声音，但起码有一席之地，习下X上派傻逼也越来越少而且变成笑话一样的存在，中国完蛋之后分裂有望。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-24",
      "agree_count": 5,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "657818",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "天天吃腊肉",
        "uid": "111737"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t只希望主打匿名的本站能对<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>更友好一些, 现在虽说不是<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>完全不能注册但用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>注册真的太累人.<br/>\n当然我也理解这是中共故意用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>在本站恶意发言导致的, 但如果本站因为中共故意用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>在本站恶意发言就太严格的限制Tor注册, 那中共也就真的达到(削弱用户匿名措施的)目的了.<br/>\n建议并呼吁站方和无需高强度匿名(比如身在海外)的本站常驻用户可以定期测试用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>注册发言的用户体验, 以此保证真正需要匿名的(类似编程随想之类的)用户可以全程用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG93bmxvYWQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.torproject.org/zh-CN/download/\">Tor</a>注册本站.<br/>\n我是疯狂用<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdXBwb3J0LnRvcnByb2plY3Qub3JnL3poLUNOL2dsb3NzYXJ5L25ldy10b3ItY2lyY3VpdC1mb3ItdGhpcy1zaXRlLw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://support.torproject.org/zh-CN/glossary/new-tor-circuit-for-this-site/\">Tor的新链路功能</a>才注册成功的.<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90Yi1tYW51YWwudG9ycHJvamVjdC5vcmcvemgtQ04vbWFuYWdpbmctaWRlbnRpdGllcy8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://tb-manual.torproject.org/zh-CN/managing-identities/\">Tor的新链路功能使用方法</a>.\t\t</div>",
